'''Note:''' [[GPG]] is not a standard part of [[Mac OS X]] so must be installed separately; see "[[Installing GPG 1.4.10 on Mac OS X 10.6.2 Snow Leopard]]" for more information.

<pre lang="shell">$ wget http://www.complang.org/ragel/ragel-6.6.tar.gz \
       http://www.complang.org/ragel/ragel-6.6.tar.gz.asc
$ gpg --verify ragel-6.6.tar.gz.asc ragel-6.6.tar.gz
$ tar xzvf ragel-6.6.tar.gz
$ cd ragel-6.6
$ ./configure
$ make
$ cd test
$ ./runtests
$ cd ..
$ sudo make install</pre>

Nice to see that `runtests` works now out of the box without requiring any tweaks to the include paths.
